The paper deals with the control of mobile agents to form rigid formations and achieve motion control. This falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves the design of controllers for achieving specific objectives, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). The paper also involves mathematical analysis and experiments, which could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV).
